             was indicted for <rs id="t18220220-147-off801" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-147-off801" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-147-off801" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
